snippet.title: Johnny Depp vs. Amber Heard: Petition to FIRE Mera from AQUAMAN 2?!
snippet.description:
Is the internet's opinion on Johnny Depp vs. Amber Heard swinging toward Depp? Many are claiming to support Depp now in light of some photographic evidence that was meant to support Heard's claims... but apparently backfired. Now a Change-org petition has been created by fans calling for Amber Heard to be fired as Mera in Aquaman 2... but would that actually happen?

Links -

https://boundingintocomics.com/2019/03/21/petition-created-to-remove-amber-heard-from-aquaman-2-after-johnny-depps-lawsuit/

https://meaww.com/johnny-depp-amber-heard-defamation-lawsuit-fan-support

https://meaww.com/petition-filed-amber-heard-removed-aquaman-2-johnny-depp-defamation-lawsuit

https://www.change.org/p/dc-entertainment-remove-amber-heard-from-aquaman-2
